  • Classes in ch.zh.transferclient.gui used by ch.zh.transferclient.gui 
    Class Description
    DialogDir
    This class is used to show a dialog which informs the user that a result folder has to be chosen before the the transfer-client can be activated.
    DialogFileProcessingError
    This class is used to show a dialog which informs the user that a error occurred while a file has been processed.
    DialogReceiptNotWellFormed
    This class is used to show a dialog which informs the user that a received sedex receipt file is not well formed.
    DialogSupport
    This class is used to show a dialog which informs the user about the contact details for support.
    DialogWaitingForDeactivation
    This class is used to show a dialog which informs the user that the transfer-client will be deactivated.
    Gui
    This class is used to produce a graphical user interface.

    Status fields of the GuiStart that can be used for informing the end user about the current status.
